{"tid":2244753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好浪漫 支那最美抗疫護士嫁軍人","createTime":"2020-10-15T17:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T00:30:27.000Z","uid":235814,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"91047219dd960c596869d9ad253d529f2d78f00b","tid":2244753,"uid":235814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:14:25.000Z","msg":"于鑫慧早前聲稱自己是一名護士，在新冠肺炎疫情最嚴重時，曾瞞着父母到武漢抗疫，並在康復隔離點駐守55天。她今年4月時曾登上電視台高調徵婚，表示<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">自幼崇拜解放軍，雖然沒能當上女兵，但夢想「成為一名偉大的軍嫂」。</span></span>及後經熱心人介紹，她結識了在河北某部某旅當排長的王林，並發展戀情。十一長假期間，于女到軍營探望王男，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">對方在戰友面前浪漫求婚</span></span>，過程獲多間媒體報道。報道指，王林是一名優秀的軍人，曾在朱日和沙場閱兵及多次陸軍比武中獲得嘉獎，又被評為集團軍優秀共產黨員，是不折不扣的優秀戰士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好浪漫咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇真啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2人結婚消息傳出後僅數天，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">王男</span></span>被爆料他與于女拍拖期間，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">仍跟前女友藕斷絲連。</span></span>另于女因這段三角關係曾「自殺」入院，王男為了跟于女一起，可謂不擇手段，除說了很多難堪的說話，甚至<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">威脅前女友假如不分手，便公開過去兩人拍下的性愛片段。</span></span><br />\n另一方的<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"large\">于女</span></span>，除被發現在<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"large\">網上徵婚時仍未離婚且育有一子外，又被指前往武漢前根本並非護士，而是從事行政工作，只稱得上是志願者。另網上又曝光于女與前夫欠債不還的執行裁定書，註明于女已被納入失信被執行人名單，遭限制高消費。</span></span><br />\n事件曝光後，網民指王林是卑鄙無恥之的「渣男」，女方是「老賴」。《解放軍報》亦對此發表評論，指事件令人嘆惋，「軍婚」、「軍戀」背後是許多肩負職責虧欠家庭的軍人、默默犧牲扛起家庭重擔的軍屬，是千千萬萬相愛卻相守不易的戀人，直指「這樣平凡而偉大的字眼不該被褻瀆，這些真摯的情感不該因此沾上污點。祝福每一對選擇軍戀、軍婚的愛人，軍戀不易，萬望珍惜」。"},{"pid":"a0a506d4a7cd6b20adcf0ec65d9fc594a3b6ae9f","tid":2244753,"uid":73225,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"咁其實都幾襯吖"},{"pid":"03c6f821a2a403e3244662a68a934c7142ecb180","tid":2244753,"uid":235814,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"汁 ：白粉報<br />\n但我其實睇有線中國組先 有片<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/3373604159387063/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F3373604159387063%2F%3Frefsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252Fcablechinadesk%252F%26_rdr&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2d6e29f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/3373604159387063/?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2F&amp;_rdr</a>"},{"pid":"a8eacb5b57fd4280cc5612524ec9367569869131","tid":2244753,"uid":118120,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:21:08.000Z","msg":"成個共產黨都係呢D 金玉其外既垃圾"},{"pid":"fed3c4112c9093e80a27d8a1d2dd1748010f0a4f","tid":2244753,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0a506d4a7cd6b20adcf0ec65d9fc594a3b6ae9f","tid":2244753,"uid":73225,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"咁其實都幾襯吖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"正想咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f07150e1e9904f6128b2aa734528e842f4da3ef","tid":2244753,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"臭雞配playboy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e4698cf22e6d7a3f69e45c4d097e7c89cdca67","tid":2244753,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8eacb5b57fd4280cc5612524ec9367569869131","tid":2244753,"uid":118120,"like":16,"disl